Title: Schurch S. cerevesiae Highly Replicated Bulk RNA-Seq Counts
Description: Count matrix for bulk RNA-sequencing dataset from 86 S. cerevisiae samples in two conditions. The data was originally produced to benchmark the performance of tools for differnential expression analysis. It comes from the paper by Schurch et al. (2016). The first condition is the wild type. The second condition is a Snf2 knockout cell line.
